name: Hegemonic Bald
description:
It´s a start, an hegemonic bald. In other words, a blank page to start this journey.
The shape, the portrait as the subconscious of the artists' mood.
Thoughts, frustrations, joy and sorrows expressed on brush strokes and ramifications.
Follow me on the process of creating faces and acquiring countenance.
Support the process and the community of the portraits

2309 x 3862 pixels
